[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "抱歉，尤蒂爾。你可以過來一下嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "怎麼了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "啊──那個……該怎麼說呢。總之，你來就知道了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……？ 蘭薩弗那傢伙是怎麼了？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "所以說，我無法讓像妳這樣的人進入城裡。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "為何……為何要藏匿龍族！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "那是災厄！是應該要毀滅的存在啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "就算妳那麼說──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "怎麼了，克菈兒？這女孩怎麼了？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "啊，尤蒂爾。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "這個人，一直堅持要跟碧龍見面──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0053.wav"], "content": "你就是跟龍族締結契約的尤蒂爾對吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "妾身名為天音！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是以「沒有龍族存在的世界」為目標的奇蹟之神子！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我有聽說過。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "在以滅絕龍族為目標的小國，有個被稱為「奇蹟之神子」的人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那位神子，似乎是過去被龍族毀滅的部落裡唯一的生還者。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以才叫奇蹟之神子……嗎。這麼小的孩子……好厲害喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "什麼！？別把妾身當小孩子！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "妾身已經24歲。是個有身份地位的大人了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦咦！？是、是嗎……那真是抱歉……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "知道就好！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "呃……所以剛才是說什麼……啊──對了、對了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "龍族以強大力量屠殺人類，是會招來不幸，宛如災厄般的存在。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "所以妾身想要在這座有龍族居住的城中，尋找那些傢伙的弱點！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "哦，那妳還是去找其他人吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "知道是那種理由後，怎麼可能乖乖讓妳進城啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "唔……你們還是要袒護龍族嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是，妾身不會因這點小事作罷的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "直到你們打開大門為止，不管要坐幾天，妾身都不會離去！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然妳這麼說，不過待在這裡好幾天真的沒問題嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "還是在造成騷動前先回去……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "找出龍族的弱點才是最重要的！那正是吾等之宿願！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以沒問題……大概！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "唉……演變成麻煩的局面了。該怎麼辦呢，尤蒂爾。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "……我明白了。既然妳都那麼說了，好吧，就讓妳進城。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "喂、喂喂……這樣好嗎！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "要是耶夢加得發生什麼事的話……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "的確，龍族或許也有像她所說的宛如災厄般的一面。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "但是，也有像耶夢加得那樣的存在。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要真正相處過，她就會瞭解，世上也是有友善的龍族的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而且，雖然這完全是我的直覺，不過她是個很直率的人對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "我覺得只要談過，彼此之間就能互相理解的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "雖然我很擔心……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0028.wav"], "content": "但既然是尤蒂爾的決定，我會照辦的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0049.wav"], "content": "走吧，天音。我帶妳參觀城裡，跟我來。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "啊，這一刻終於到來了……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "妾身要實現沒有龍族存在的世界！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110041011, "title": "奇蹟之神子天音 (110041011)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0053.wav"], "content": "唔！找到你們了，尤蒂爾，蘭薩弗！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "你們為什麼老是要逃跑！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "今天一定要讓你們說出龍族的弱點！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "所、所以我們昨天不就說過了？我們不知道弱點的事啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "多少告訴妾身一點吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "告訴妾身毀滅龍族的線索！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "……啊，對了，克菈兒有拜託我去幫她忙！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "剩下就交給你了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "啊！蘭薩弗你太卑鄙了！克菈兒才不會拜託你去幫忙吧！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "尤蒂爾！快告訴我龍族的事！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "嗯……我說天音啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我覺得，比起毀滅龍族，還是互相理解──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "唔！你又在講那種話了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0029.wav"], "content": "尤蒂爾的玩笑話，妾身已經聽膩了！　", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "好好改改自己的想法吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "若是無論如何都不肯回答，妾身今天就去問克菈兒！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "啊，克菈兒正在做菜，不要打擾她比較……唔，已經走了嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "唉……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "天音。妳今天也一整天都在城裡奔走嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "嗯，是啊……可是弱點的事，今天也毫無收穫……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "本來還以為來到這裡的話……就能掌握線索，實現沒有龍族存在的世界呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……妳會那麼努力，是因為妳是奇蹟之神子嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "還是說……因為龍族毀滅了妳的部落，所以妳對他們心懷怨恨呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "怨恨……憎恨嗎？並不是說沒有，但有點不同。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妾身的國家……聚集了像妾身一樣被龍族傷害的受害者，你知道這件事吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "有人被奪走戀人，有人被奪走孩子……有人被奪走雙親。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "那樣的人，在妾身的國家多到數不清。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "妾身不希望，再有跟吾等一樣傷心的人了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "……原來如此。妳之所以想毀滅龍族，是出自那顆為人著想的心啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "不過，結果就像你看到的一敗塗地。可是，妾身是不會放棄的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "問一個人問不到的話，就問10個人！問10個人問不到的話，就問100個人！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "只有不屈不撓地行動下去了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "好！既然已經下定決心，妾身要繼續去打聽了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "蘭薩弗那傢伙，應該也已經幫忙完了吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "唔喔，天音……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "等一下，今天我還要為明天的早飯作準備──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "你平常根本不做準備的吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "別說了，在那邊坐好，跟妾身坦白吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "嗯……實在是敵不過天音的熱忱啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "該怎麼辦才好呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110041012, "title": "天音的思念 (110041012)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "對、對了！想到一個好主意了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "為什麼之前都沒發現這件事呢！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "嗯？妳想到了什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "要找出龍族的弱點，直接去問龍族不是最快嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "咦……不，我覺得這好像有點──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "龍族不可能親自告訴妳自己的弱點吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "放棄吧。妳只會被他給吹飛的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "哼。即使如此，妾身還是要去！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "為了不再讓人因龍族而悲傷！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "嗚哇──────！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "我早就說了吧……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0039.wav"], "content": "妳、妳還好嗎，天音？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "沒、沒事。只是稍微被吹飛了而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "更重要的是，妾身問到了！──那傢伙的弱點！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦……！？耶夢加得他告訴妳了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "沒錯！他確實說了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "他的弱點就是「讓人讚不絕口的料理」！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "看來人類會覺得美味的成分，對龍族的身體是有毒的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "妾身馬上去進行料理修行！廚房借我一下！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "不管怎麼想，那都是碧龍的謊言吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "天、天音她個性率直嘛。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "可能很容易就會相信別人的謊話。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "總、總算完成美味的料理了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "接下來，只要讓那隻龍族吃下這個……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "美味的料理……？妳是說這紫色的詭異物體嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "第、第一次做這樣算好了吧！這道菜是以味道取勝的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "天音，我想……料理大概不是耶夢加得的弱點。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？可、可是他確實說……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "那應該是耶夢加得的玩笑話什麼的吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "妾……妾身、被騙了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "可、可惡啊──！碧龍那傢伙！！喂，碧龍啊！快說出真正的弱點！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "嗚哇──────！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……這小妞還沒受夠教訓啊。不過只論膽量與行動力的話，她倒是挺厲害的呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "別在那佩服了，快去幫幫她吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100004_story/VO_CHR_100004_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "再這樣下去，她人都不知道要飛到哪去了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100004_01.png", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "可是……耶夢加得那傢伙……到底打算怎麼處理天音的事啊……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110041013, "title": "碧龍的玩笑 (110041013)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "嗚哇────────！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210001_story/VO_DRG_210001_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "毫無記取教訓呢，人類之子。是欲遭吾吹飛幾回才肯罷休？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0026.wav"], "content": "哈啊、哈啊……再、再來幾次也沒用……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "在問到你的弱點前，妾身無論如何都不會放棄的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210001_story/VO_DRG_210001_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……吾應已明言。吾之弱點，乃龍尾受到擦拭一事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "擦了尾巴也只是變乾淨而已不是嗎？你這大騙子！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "怎麼了，耶夢加得。你好像很開心的樣子。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "此種人類，吾並無感到厭惡。既率直，亦內心純潔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "這表示，你很中意天音嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "碧龍很中意……妾身？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0034.wav"], "content": "不可能！ 不可能會有那種事！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "將妾身的故鄉、家人……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "破壞殆盡後全部奪走的那個災厄，怎麼可能……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……至少耶夢加得沒做過那種事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為他──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210001_story/VO_DRG_210001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "尤蒂爾，無須否定此事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210001_story/VO_DRG_210001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "確實，吾等乃人稱災厄之存在。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "僅是振翼即掀起風暴，若咆哮則使萬物崩滅。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "正因生來即具強大力量，確實世間亦有龍族，視汝等為弱者，並蹂躪以暴行。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210001_story/VO_DRG_210001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "而吾之樣貌，與吾所述之輩並無二致。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "遭奪盡一切之人視吾為復仇對象，亦是理所當然。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "耶夢加得……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……吾言盡於此。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若無意再遭吾吹飛，則立刻離開此處便是。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0039.wav"], "content": "天音，妳沒事吧？妳的臉色看起來似乎不太好……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……妾身，好像有些混亂了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是關於耶夢加得的事吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……龍族奪走了妾身的一切。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "要是放任他們，世界就會到處充滿擁有相同遭遇的人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "所以妾身一定要讓他們從這世上消失……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "但是，那個碧龍卻會笑、會生氣，也會與人交談……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "跟吾等人類，沒有兩樣……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "難不成妾身……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不只不知道他的弱點，根本是對他一無所知嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "……既然這樣，妳就多跟耶夢加得說說話吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "為了更加瞭解他。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "……說的、也是。妾身得更加明白才行。關於龍族的性情、弱點……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "以及……他的本質。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110041014, "title": "一無所知 (110041014)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210001_01_out/VO_DRG_210001_01_OUT_0005.wav"], "content": "……有何指教，人類之子？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "今日不如往常般，弱點長弱點短地大肆叫嚷了？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……碧龍啊。妾身已經搞不清楚你究竟是怎樣的存在了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喔？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "碧龍，妾身認為……你與襲擊了妾身部落的惡龍不同。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是，毀滅了妾身部落的元兇，仍是……龍族。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "無法原諒你們的心情，也是真的。妾身到底該如何是好……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……吾之弱點為「逆鱗」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吾等之龍鱗中，僅有一片為方向相反之存在。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "該龍鱗即是逆鱗，為吾等之，弱點。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "咦──等、等一下！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0053.wav"], "content": "為何！？為何，如此重要的事要告訴妾身！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……一時心血來潮罷了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "現在，汝欲有何作為？是否將吾殺死？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "怎、怎麼會……妾身……妾身……！嗚……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0039.wav"], "content": "天音……妳還好嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "妾身……知道那傢伙的弱點了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "現在或許能殺掉他也說不定……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "但是，妾身發現到了一件事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那傢伙與人類，即使樣貌不同，但都是擁有「心」的生物。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "要是單方面地毀滅對方，妾身就會成為與引起災厄的那些傢伙一樣的存在。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "但妾身是奇蹟之神子。到底該怎麼辦……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……那就，兩者都保護不就好了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "兩者都……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "守護龍族，也保護人類。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "由天音創造出不用毀滅龍族，也不會有人受到龍族傷害的世界。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "妳一定做得到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "因為天音不是一般的神子，而是奇蹟之神子啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！呼、呵呵呵。嗯，說得也是呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "謝謝你，尤蒂爾。……一起回去吧，到碧龍那裡。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "碧龍啊，妾身已經決定了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "妾身不毀滅你了！要與你走上共存之路！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210001_01_out/VO_DRG_210001_01_OUT_0002.wav"], "content": "……呵，汝真心認為如此為上？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吾等往後亦有可能於此世界某處襲擊人類喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "當然，因為妾身已經決定好了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "要在不毀滅你們的情況下，將人們從悲傷中拯救出來！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "若是出現了會襲擊人類的傢伙，就由妾身來支配他！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "這樣就全部解決了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "哈哈哈哈！竟揚言欲支配龍族！果然有趣啊，人類之子！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "既然如此，吾便以此雙眼，見證汝非比尋常的野心吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "唔！碧龍啊，這次特別禮遇，就允許你成為妾身的朋友吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210001_01.png", "speakerName": "耶夢加得", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110041_story/VO_CHR_110041_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "嗚哇────────！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110041_01.png", "speakerName": "天音", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110041015, "title": "奇蹟之神子，野心的決意 (110041015)"}]